#: ../../../fb/sh7760fb.rst:35
msgid "SH7760:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../fb/sh7760fb.rst:36
msgid ""
"Video data is fetched via the DMABRG DMA engine, so you have to configure "
"the SH DMAC for DMABRG mode (write 0x94808080 to the DMARSRA register "
"somewhere at boot)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../fb/sh7760fb.rst:40
msgid ""
"PFC registers PCCR and PCDR must be set to peripheral mode. (write zeros to "
"both)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../fb/sh7760fb.rst:43
msgid ""
"The driver does NOT do the above for you since board setup is, well, job of "
"the board setup code."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../fb/sh7760fb.rst:47
msgid "2. Panel definitions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../fb/sh7760fb.rst:48
msgid ""
"The LCDC must explicitly be told about the type of LCD panel attached.  Data "
"must be wrapped in a \"struct sh7760fb_platdata\" and passed to the driver "
"as platform_data."
msgstr ""

